Web Interface - Part 2 Design Task

1. SongServlet:
	- initialize searchPool
	- fire executor SearchQuery
	- do searchByMethod
	- return a JSONArray which has all similars_song based on artist query key in
	- See example below:
	
	
	"artist": "Busta Rhymes",						<-- query typed in for search
      "similars": [
        {
          "artist": "DJ Quik",						<-- return int html page - artist title
          "trackId": "TRAAMJY128F92F5919",			
          "title": "Born and Raised In Compton"		<-- return in html page - artist's title
        },
        {
          "artist": "Sticky Fingaz",
          "trackId": "TRAAZBD128F427A97D",
          "title": "Oh My God"
        }
        
        
        



